  "detailed_description": "A simple and fun game of collecting food, the more you collect, the faster the game will become, but be careful, because not everything is food.<br />\r\n  <br />\r\n  Use the arrow keys on your keyboard or mouse to move the player sideways to collect food.<br />\r\n  <br />\r\n  Collect to increase your Score:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n Chicken, 3 points score<br />\r\n Burger,   2 point score<br />\r\n Pizza,     1 point score<br />\r\n Cake,     1 point score<br />\r\n<br />\r\n The bowling ball reduces your health!",
